        "TileImage": "$($repository 22a19308-5b21-4e80-a915-467ebc43a1de).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to Mumbai, 47.\r\rYour task is to take down these two seemingly innocent people.\r\rThey are the leaders of a infamous gang that has gone into hiding since the late 2010s. After their entire crew left and went into hiding, they went into hiding. Hiding here in Mumbai living out the rest of their lives with no worries in the world, soon all of their past actions will catch up to them. They need to pay for what they did to the ICA. Find them and do what you do best. \r\rGoodluck, 47.",
